* Process
  - `master` updates over time
  - pull `master` weekly
  - rebase `staging`
  - `flake update`
  - push staging
  - merge PR
  - repeat

* Script
  @code bash
  git clone $repo --depth 1 . --single-branch --branch staging
  git pull origin master
  git push
  @end

